description: STB Chain (STB) is currently the world’s leading application of Blockchain technology in software, and is a decentralised, tamper-proof and completely traceable rights verification trading system. STB covers multi-field technology applications, a few examples being Cloud Computing, Big Data, AI and SaaS cloud services. Scientific and technological achievement-based. Our goal is to establish a new ecosystem of distributed application software services with no borders. With the combination of Blockchain technology and the software industry, an effective copyright protection and trading platform will be established.
name: STB Chain
